WEBVTT

00:00:00.757 --> 00:00:04.244
Dvestapedesetdevet miliona

00:00:04.244 --> 00:00:10.551
stopet hiljada petsto sedamdeset
kilograma papirnih ubrusa

00:00:10.551 --> 00:00:12.438
koriste Amerikanci

00:00:12.438 --> 00:00:14.497
godišnje.

00:00:16.543 --> 00:00:19.164
Ako bismo mogli - ispravka,
pogrešna cifra -

00:00:19.164 --> 00:00:21.515
6 milijardi se upotrebi svake godine.

00:00:21.515 --> 00:00:24.618
Ako bismo mogli redukovati
upotrebu papirnih ubrusa,

00:00:24.618 --> 00:00:27.800
jedan papirni ubrus po osobi dnevno,

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:34.421
259,105,570 kilograma
papira bismo uštedeli.